<p>Lucky Chucky, a 3br/2ba would probably end up around $400-700,000 after land, construction, etc. It is a pretty high end luxury good. At most I would spend 3-6 months per year because I do like the big city, etc. It really depends what you want for your lifestyle design. Not sure if it would be exactly what you would want.</p>
